snippet.title: Dreamfall Chapters Book 5 END (Full Gameplay) HD
snippet.description:
Full unedited game play of Dreamfall Chapters Book 5 - The Longest Journey.

I try my best to explore the maps and listen to the dialogue. Book 5 answers many questions about Dreamfall but many questions still remain. Support the developers by buying the game so we can play a sequel.

★ Get Dreamfall Chapters on Steam @ http://store.steampowered.com/app/237850/
★ Check out the 'Play To Win' game play channel @ http://bit.ly/1V3nd2n

If you like what you see, please subscribe and thumbs up! It really means a lot and helps me out a bunch. Thanks!

Support the stream! Donations are welcome @ https://www.paypal.me/SayHello

Thanks for watching!
